                                (98 . 35)
                                (2 . 35)
                                (79 . 90]
                 (TRANSFORMED-POLY-POINTS (HTMLTEST.TRANSFORM-POINTS POLY-POINTS (P-TO-CP -20)
                                                 (P-TO-CP -20)
                                                 (TIMES 3 *CENTIPOINTS-PER-POINT*)
